{
  "texts": [
    "By contrast, DE is limited because it often \"locks\" one into high yield for only a single substrate or closely related ones, as the final variant is generally a single optimized sequence.",
    "Here, we observe an emergent advantage inherent to ALDE: since sequences that balance exploration and exploitation for a given task are proposed, they can be serendipitously proficient at related tasks.",
    "ALDE is enabled by several recent advancements in biotechnology.",
    "For the initial library constructed using degenerate codons, highthroughput sequencing was necessary to identify the sequences of variants in each well.",
    "For this work we utilized LevSeq 43, 60, a method that leverages real-time nanopore sequencing."
  ]
}